intro_tutorial:
    clear_dialog
    //run transition generic_sunset
    run transition title
    talk poppy talk "Hi everyone, it's me, Poppy! Creator of such games as <span class='writtenText'>'Parsnip'</span>, <span class='writtenText'>'The Testimony of Trixie Glimmer Smith'</span> and <span class='writtenText'>'Madden NFL 2022'</span>!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "I just wanted to let you know that Lovely Lady RPG takes place over FOUR days, you're living the first one now!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "Like all women, Ghost can only make a maximum of six <span class='prompt'>ACTIONS</span> per day!"
    talk poppy talk "Be careful though, some things can cause Ghost to spend additional <span class='prompt'>ACTIONS</span> to complete an objective!"
    talk poppy talk "When Ghost uses all of her <span class='prompt'>ACTIONS</span> she will go to bed! What a sleepy girl!"
    clear_dialog
    run transition tutorial_hud
    talk poppy talk "You can see which day you are on, how many <span class='prompt'>ACTIONS</span> you have left, and how much money Ghost is carrying here!"
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant tutorial_system
    talk poppy talk "You can use this to access the system menu, where you can do exciting things like adjust volume sliders, press the exit button etc"
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant tutorial_character
    talk poppy talk "You can use this cute little button to access Ghost's inventory, quest log, gamer achievements and skills menu!"
    talk poppy talk "You just received your first quest, so perhaps you should have a look at the log now, in case you've already gotten confused!"
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant tutorial_auto
    talk poppy talk "You can use this button to toggle autoplay on and off, if you're tired of clicking the continue button."
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant tutorial_skip
    talk poppy talk "This button to fast forward through the text I wrote, if you hate me and want me to die. Whine whine whine! Perhaps only use this button in your speedruns?"
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant tutorial_history
    talk poppy talk "And the final button to view any older text!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "That's all for now, have fun!"
    jump intro_home

intro_tutorial_outro:
    clear_dialog
    run transition title
    talk poppy talk "Hi again! This is the last time I'll bother you, I promise!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "I thought I'd let you know that from this point onwards the map will have multiple tasks for you to take care of, some of which might disappear if you leave them too long!"
    talk poppy talk "You won't have time to take care of everything, so be careful, and prioritise things you think *will* be important! The *true* Lovely Lady RPG starts here!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "You may have also already noticed that the space key allows you to progress through dialogue without the need to click! How handy!"
    talk poppy talk "Likewise your number keys can be used to select choices!"
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "The game will autosave occasionally. Please do your best not to close the game while this is happening!"
    clear_dialog
    talk lovely talk "Apologies darling, one small question before you go: how do we *load* our game?"
    talk poppy talk "Y- you aren't meant to be talking back to me! I'm non diegetic!"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk nasty talk "Who the fuck cares if she's die ah genetic or not. I'm going to fuck the tutorial character."
        roll intro_tutorial_fuck_nasty nasty 90 "You *should* try to fuck the tutorial character, Nasty Girl. [Try to convince the tutorial character she should get with Nasty Girl]":
            success "":
                set data.intro.fuckNarrator true
                "You do a sort of, smutty homosexual wink at the tutorial character."
                clear_dialog
                talk lovely talk "You two are simply awful. Allow me to prostate myself at thine feet and apologise on their behalf, tutorial character."
                talk poppy talk "Sorry Nasty Girl, but I really need to explain how to load the game right now, since Lovely Lady seems to have too much brain damage to work it out for herself!"
            failure "":
                "You do a sort of, smutty homosexual wink at the tutorial character, only you do it with both eyes, so it's more of a blink than a wink, and blinks really aren't all that sexy."
                clear_dialog
                talk lovely talk "You two are simply awful. Allow me to prostate myself at thine feet and apologise on their behalf, tutorial character."
                talk poppy talk "Sorry Nasty Girl, but I really need to explain how to load the game right now, since Lovely Lady seems to have too much brain damage to work it out for herself!"
        "Sorry Nasty Girl, that's a little bit too masturbatory.":
            run skip
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "You can load your game by going to the main menu and hitting continue or load! You can save between scenes, but try not to make any mistakes anyway, okay!"
    talk nasty talk "Load. Cum."
    clear_dialog
    talk poppy talk "This brings me to my final word of advice! Don't let Nasty Girl talk you into doing anything I wouldn't do!"
    talk orb talk "Sage advice."
    talk poppy talk "No! It really isn't! I have very poor impulse control!"
    clear_dialog
    if $data.intro.fuckNarrator:
        talk poppy talk "Anyway, I'll leave you alone now. Bye gang."
        run transition_instant generic_black
        clear_dialog
        wait 4000
        run transition_instant title
        talk poppy talk "Oh, and Nasty Girl. DM me."
        talk nasty talk "Yes hahaha yesssss!"
    else:
        talk poppy talk "Anyway, I'll leave you alone now. Bye gang."
    clear_dialog
    run transition_instant generic_black
    animate #narrat-app narrat-screenshake
    wait 4000
    run transition_instant generic_street
    animate #narrat-app narrat-screenshake
    talk lovely talk "Goodness, I feel like I blacked out for a moment. Did something happen?"
    talk nasty talk "Uuuugh. I haven't felt this disoriented since I mainlined medicinal ethanol with the lads."
    choice:
        talk orb talk "It wasn't canon. Don't worry."
        "Yawn! I'm too sleepy to worry. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            "Regardless of how unworried you are, you are sleepy. Waking up with an orb embedded in your chest has not done wonders for your sleep schedule, and it is time for the debt to be paid."
            jump dream

